FBIS4-17007 "drsov077_b_94037" FBIS-SOV-94-077 Daily Report 21 Apr 1994 RUSSIA NATIONAL AFFAIRS Economic Issues Yeltsin Greets Moscow Bankers' Conference Yeltsin Greets Moscow Bankers' Conference LD2104083494 Moscow Mayak Radio Network in Russian 0800 GMT 21 Apr 94 LD2104083494 Moscow Mayak Radio Network Russian BFN [Text] Russian President Yeltsin has sent greetings to the congress of the Association of Russian Banks, which opened in Moscow today. The greetings say: Russia's economy needs an effective payments system, more active involvement of commercial banks in investment projects, expansion of the banking services sector, and an improvement in quality. We believe that these issues will be a topic for professional debate at your congress. The president wished the congress productive work.
